long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: As a Kanye West fan myself, I always enjoy a good Kanye Quote. With this extension, you can generate random Kanye quotes whenever you want! From "Imma let you finish" to that one quote about Lady Gaga and Kodak, you can enjoy seeing some classic lines from the famous music artist formerly known as Kanye West.
